snippet.title: Midnight Fight Express | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: humblegames.com/midnightfightexpress

Fight your way across the city in a brutal romp that mixes old school brawlers, fast-paced motion-captured combat, and customizable skills.

Use fists, feet, knives, pipes, pistols, machine guns, and more to wade through piles of enemies on your way to victory.

Follow Humble Games: 
TW: https://bit.ly/HumbleGames_TW 
IG: https://bit.ly/HumbleGames_IG 
FB: https://bit.ly/HumbleGames_FB

Subscribe to our newsletter: https://www.humblegames.com/
